        "shortCode": "CWDsDzkB72n",
        "caption": "[HIGH PERFORMANCE SWIMMING SEMINAR]🏊🏊‍♂️🏊‍♀️\n\nSwimming Club MMU Melaka is pleased to announce that we are having an online swimming seminar which aims to provide students an opportunity to learn the mistakes that are commonly done in swimming. With this guidance, students are able to improve their water confindence with a greater understanding of each stroke and continue improving. \n\nWe are honoured to have Mr Ahmad Hazri Mohamed Aris as our speaker, who is a Level 1 & 2 Coach with the American Swimming Coach Association (ASCA), and a certified Lifesaver Instructor who holds the Award of Merit Lifesaving Qualification with Life Saving Society of Malaysia (LSSM). He is also a certified Lifesaver with the International Lifesaving Society (ILS).\n\nThe High Performance Swimming Seminar would take place on;\nDate: 4th December 2021 (Saturday)\nTime: 11am-12pm\nPlatform: Google Meet\nParticipation of the event is free of charge with a compliment of RM5 KFC voucher 🍗 and an exciting lucky draw is awaiting you! 🎉\n\nHurry up and register on the following link in our bio by 1st December 2021✨",
