        "caption": "[MULTIMEDIA UNIVERSITY SWIMMING CLUB MERCHANDISE SALE]\n\nGreeting to all MMU students, The Multimedia University Swimming Club is proudly to present the latest merchandise as a token of appreciation to all support from members and non-members. *The T-shirt is LIMITED EDITION*. The merchandise is T-shirt that is made with micro-fiber that is extremely durable and comfortable.It also represents the ink-style and Chinese traditional style for fashion and dazzling view. The details of the t-shirt is listed as follows:\n\nSize: XS/S/M/ L / XL/XXL\nPrice: RM 35\nMethod of Collecting: Self-pickup / Delivery\n\nPre-order would be avaliable staring from *11/5/2023- 14/5/2023*\n\nThe price stated in the from .\n\nFor those that are interested, kindly fill up the google form as follows to get an order. \nhttps://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd-UnujimJySqPj-DHBO7HZQpSjUqVYehgcCSbGyGuZkBin_g/viewform?usp=sf_link\n\nFor further information, do contact:\n\nchaw hui xin (0183680722)",
