        "shortCode": "CsfjrJ1OCuC",
        "caption": "MMU OPEN SWIMMING COMPETITION\n\nDear all MMU Students, our Swimming Club Melaka Campus is proudly to present the latest event in collabration🤝 with Swimming Club Cyberjaya Campus. The event is Friendly Match Competition with Swimming Club Cyberjaya and it will be full of prizes 💸 and also mainatin our healthy lifestyle. \n\nTo help everyone get ready for the match, we will be organising a one day of training for all participants. This training session 🙆‍♂️ will be led by our Couch named  Mr. Ng Yau Kit🏊 This session is said to take place in late May or one week before the competition🗓️ where you will learn about the rules and skills for the competition📚.\n\nThe details of the friendly Match are as follows:\n\n📅 Date: 10/6/2023 (Saturday)\n🕚 Time: 8am - 5pm\n📍Venue: MMU CyberJaya Campus\n💵Registration Fee: RM 15\n\nIn addition, all food, transportation and T-shirt will be provided by our club for FREE for all participants. If anyone is interested, do registered in the follwing google form link in the bio.\n\nFor more information, do contact:\nChaw Hui Xin (President of MMU Swimming Club)\nContact No📱: 018-368 0722",
