    {
        "id": "2989433135999354415",
        "type": "Image",
        "shortCode": "Cl8mZk3BgYv",
        "caption": "𝐌𝐎𝐕𝐈𝐄𝐌𝐀𝐍𝐈𝐀 𝟎𝟎𝟏\n\nGreetings to all, \n\nThe MMU Melaka Swimming Club is pleased to announce the introduction of \"MovieMania 001,\" happening this Sunday (11 December), beginning at 7pm. We invite all mmu and non-mmu students to partake in our upcoming event as we de-stress by enjoying refreshments, watching the latest cinema delights, make new friends and have a blast before the end of the year.\n\nAdmission is free, refreshments are free, not to mention secret prizes in store for all our wonderful attendees. We encourage all to bring along your mates and enjoy the club's latest event, special for your eyes only.\n\n𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐝𝐞𝐭𝐚𝐢𝐥𝐬 𝐨𝐟 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐚𝐫𝐞 𝐚𝐬 𝐟𝐨𝐥𝐥𝐨𝐰𝐬:\n𝐃𝐚𝐭𝐞: 𝟏𝟏 𝐃𝐞𝐜𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟐 (𝐅𝐫𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐲)\n𝐓𝐢𝐦𝐞: 𝟕.𝟎𝟎 𝐩.𝐦. 𝐭𝐨 𝟏𝟎.𝟑𝟎 𝐩.𝐦.\n𝐕𝐞𝐧𝐮𝐞: 𝐌𝐒𝐌𝐗 𝟎𝟎𝟎𝟒\n\nMember: Free of charge\nNon-member: RM5\n\nIf you are interested to join us, do fill in the google form provided below:\n\nhttps://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd9ji4RNQerHoZROmi8Op3YH5OyAvmmvoB_bZ1tOXfufj5IIg/viewform?usp=pp_url\n\nNewcomers & Returning Friends are all welcome to join us. We look forward to seeing you there!\n\nShould you have any inquiries, please do not hesitate to contact:\nChaw Hui Xin (President): +60 18-368 0722\nBenny Chong (Vice President): +60 10-538 2138\nHo Yi Xuen (Vice President) :+60 12-7741405\n\nThank you.\n\nMMU Melaka Swimming Club 2022/2023",
